<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Ultimate Beauty Guide</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<style>
  body{
    margin:0;
    padding:20px;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg, #ffd6e8, #ffb6d9, #ffcfe8);
    color:#4a2c3a;
  }

  h1{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:40px;
    color:#b3006b;
    margin-bottom:30px;
    text-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  }

  .menu{
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:12px;
    margin-bottom:30px;
  }

  .menu button{
    padding:10px 18px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:25px;
    background:#fff0f7;
    color:#b3006b;
    font-weight:bold;
    cursor:pointer;
    box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.9), inset 0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  }

  .section{
    background:linear-gradient(145deg, #fff, #f7e7f0);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:25px;
    margin-bottom:25px;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 15px rgba(255,255,255,0.9),
      0 0 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.6),
      inset 0 0 12px rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }

  h2{
    margin-top:0;
    color:#b3006b;
    font-size:28px;
    text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }

  ul{
    padding-left:20px;
    line-height:1.6;
  }

  .sub{
    font-weight:bold;
    color:#8a0052;
    margin-top:10px;
  }

  /* Back to menu arrow */
  .back-arrow{
    position:fixed;
    bottom:20px;
    right:20px;
    background:#fff0f7;
    width:55px;
    height:55px;
    border-radius:50%;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    font-size:28px;
    color:#b3006b;
    cursor:pointer;
    box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(255,255,255,0.9), inset 0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  }

  .back-arrow:hover{
    transform:scale(1.1);
  }
</style>

<script>
  function scrollToMenu(){
    document.getElementById("menu").scrollIntoView({behavior:"smooth"});
  }
</script>

</head>

<body>

<h1>✨ Ultimate Beauty Guide ✨</h1>

<div id="menu" class="menu">
  <button onclick="document.getElementById('skincare').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Skincare</button>
  <button onclick="document.getElementById('makeup').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Makeup</button>
  <button onclick="document.getElementById('hair').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Haircare</button>
  <button onclick="document.getElementById('fragrance').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Fragrance</button>
  <button onclick="document.getElementById('face').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Face Shapes</button>
  <button onclick="document.getElementById('undertone').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Undertones</button>
  <button onclick="document.getElementById('aesthetic').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Aesthetic Styles</button>
  <button onclick="document.getElementById('glowup').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Glow-Up Tips</button>
</div>

<!-- SKINCARE -->
<div id="skincare" class="section">
  <h2>💖 Skincare Guide</h2>

  <p class="sub">Daily Routine</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Cleanser</b> — Gel for oily, cream for dry.</li>
    <li><b>Toner</b> — Hydrating toners > alcohol toners.</li>
    <li><b>Serum</b> — Vitamin C AM, Retinol PM.</li>
    <li><b>Moisturizer</b> — Gel for oily, cream for dry.</li>
    <li><b>Sunscreen</b> — SPF 30+ every day.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">Advanced Steps</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Essence</b> — Adds hydration + glow.</li>
    <li><b>Exfoliation</b> — AHA for glow, BHA for pores.</li>
    <li><b>Face Masks</b> — Clay for oily, sheet masks for dry.</li>
    <li><b>Facial Oils</b> — Rosehip, squalane, argan.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">Skin Concerns</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Acne</b> — Salicylic acid, benzoyl peroxide.</li>
    <li><b>Hyperpigmentation</b> — Vitamin C, niacinamide.</li>
    <li><b>Aging</b> — Retinol, peptides, sunscreen.</li>
    <li><b>Redness</b> — Centella, azelaic acid.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- MAKEUP -->
<div id="makeup" class="section">
  <h2>💄 Makeup Guide</h2>

  <p class="sub">Base Makeup</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Primer</b> — Blurring, hydrating, mattifying.</li>
    <li><b>Foundation</b> — Dewy, matte, natural finishes.</li>
    <li><b>Concealer</b> — Brightening vs. full coverage.</li>
    <li><b>Contour</b> — Cream for natural, powder for defined.</li>
    <li><b>Blush</b> — Cream = youthful, powder = long‑lasting.</li>
    <li><b>Highlighter</b> — Champagne for warm, icy for cool.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">Eye Makeup</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Eyeshadow</b> — Matte for depth, shimmer for glam.</li>
    <li><b>Eyeliner</b> — Wing shapes for each eye type.</li>
    <li><b>Mascara</b> — Curling, volumizing, lengthening.</li>
    <li><b>Lashes</b> — Natural, wispy, dramatic, cat‑eye.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">Lip Makeup</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Lip Liner</b> — Overline subtly for fullness.</li>
    <li><b>Lipstick</b> — Matte, satin, gloss, tint.</li>
    <li><b>Gloss</b> — Clear, shimmer, plumping.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">Popular Makeup Styles</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Soft Glam</b> — Warm tones, fluffy lashes.</li>
    <li><b>Clean Girl</b> — Dewy skin, glossy lips.</li>
    <li><b>Douyin Makeup</b> — Bright under‑eye, glossy blush.</li>
    <li><b>Latte Makeup</b> — Bronze, warm, creamy tones.</li>
    <li><b>Old Money</b> — Matte skin, soft neutrals.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- HAIRCARE -->
<div id="hair" class="section">
  <h2>💆 Haircare & Styling</h2>

  <p class="sub">Hair Types</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Straight</b> — Lightweight products.</li>
    <li><b>Wavy</b> — Curl creams + diffusing.</li>
    <li><b>Curly</b> — Hydration + leave‑ins.</li>
    <li><b>Coily</b> — Oils + protective styles.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">Hair Health</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Use heat protectant.</li>
    <li>Deep condition weekly.</li>
    <li>Trim every 8–12 weeks.</li>
    <li>Silk pillowcases reduce frizz.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">Popular Hairstyles</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Soft waves.</li>
    <li>High ponytail.</li>
    <li>Messy bun.</li>
    <li>Layered butterfly cut.</li>
    <li>Glass hair (super sleek).</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- FRAGRANCE -->
<div id="fragrance" class="section">
  <h2>🌺 Fragrance Guide</h2>

  <p class="sub">Fragrance Families</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Floral</b> — Rose, jasmine, peony.</li>
    <li><b>Fresh</b> — Citrus, aquatic, clean.</li>
    <li><b>Sweet</b> — Vanilla, caramel.</li>
    <li><b>Woody</b> — Sandalwood, cedar.</li>
    <li><b>Spicy</b> — Amber, cinnamon.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">How to Apply</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Pulse points: wrists, neck, behind ears.</li>
    <li>Do not rub wrists together.</li>
    <li>Layer lotion + perfume for longevity.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- FACE SHAPES -->
<div id="face" class="section">
  <h2>🌸 Beauty by Face Shape</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Round</b> — Angular contour, lifted blush.</li>
    <li><b>Oval</b> — Most styles suit this shape.</li>
    <li><b>Square</b> — Soft curls, rounded brows.</li>
    <li><b>Heart</b> — Soft lips, balanced eyes.</li>
    <li><b>Diamond</b> — Highlight forehead + chin.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- UNDERTONES -->
<div id="undertone" class="section">
  <h2>🎨 Undertones & Color Matching</h2>

  <p class="sub">Undertone Types</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Cool</b> — Pink, blue, red.</li>
    <li><b>Warm</b> — Yellow, golden, peach.</li>
    <li><b>Neutral</b> — Mix of both.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="sub">How to Check</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Vein test: blue = cool, green = warm.</li>
    <li>Jewelry test: silver = cool, gold = warm.</li>
    <li>White shirt test: white = cool, cream = warm.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- AESTHETICS -->
<div id="aesthetic" class="section">
  <h2>🌷 Aesthetic Beauty Styles</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><b>Soft Girl</b> — Pink blush, glossy lips, fluttery lashes.</li>
    <li><b>Clean Girl</b> — Slick bun, dewy skin, minimal makeup.</li>
    <li><b>Coquette</b> — Ribbons, soft curls, rosy cheeks.</li>
    <li><b>Old Money</b> — Matte neutrals, elegant hair.</li>
    <li><b>Douyin</b> — Bright under‑eye, glossy blush, sparkles.</li>
    <li><b>Y2K</b> — Frosted lips, thin brows, shimmer.</li>
    <li><b>Latte</b> — Warm browns, bronzed skin.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- GLOW UP -->
<div id="glowup" class="section">
  <h2>✨ Glow-Up Tips</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Drink water consistently.</li>
    <li>Sleep 7–9 hours.</li>
    <li>Use SPF daily.</li>
    <li>Exfoliate weekly.</li>
    <li>Keep brows shaped.</li>
    <li>Use lip balm often.</li>
    <li>Maintain a routine.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- BACK TO MENU BUTTON -->
<div class="back-arrow" onclick="scrollToMenu()">⬆</div>

</body>
</html>
